desc: Online sales of premium artisanal Authentic Korean kimchi (Kim chee) such as napa cabbage kimchi and daikon radish kimchi or Kkakdugi and pickled vegetables, pickled daikon radish (famous as Fried Chicken Pickle), Danmuji Yellow Pickled Radish for sushi or kimball, Korean Pickled Garlic in Soy Sauce.
